%% =============================================================================
%% Dynamic Trip Page — System Architecture Sequence Diagram
%% =============================================================================
%% Purpose: Shows the three primary data flows between Member, Mobile App,
%%          BFF API, Write Queue, Notion API, and Notion DBs.
%%
%% Flows:
%%   1. Trip Page Load    — GET request chain through BFF to Notion, with polling
%%   2. Approve Component — Optimistic UI + write queue + task auto-creation
%%   3. Post Comment      — Write queue + comment creation + task auto-creation
%%
%% Assumptions:
%%   [A1] Write Queue enforces 2 req/sec to stay within Notion's 3 req/sec limit
%%        while leaving headroom for read operations.
%%   [A2] 60-second polling is the V1 real-time strategy (V1.5 adds SSE).
%%   [A3] Task Dashboard writes are fire-and-forget — failures do not block
%%        the member action (retry 3x with backoff, then log and move on).
%%   [A4] Component Comments are a separate Notion DB (Mar 13 decision).
%%   [A5] BFF returns a combined response (trip + components + comment counts)
%%        in a single response to minimize round trips to the mobile client.
%%
%% Open Questions:
%%   [Q1] Should the BFF batch the Trips + Components Notion queries in parallel,
%%        or does the 3 req/sec limit make sequential safer?
%%   [Q2] What is the exact retry backoff schedule for write queue failures?
%%   [Q3] Does the Task Dashboard deduplication (5-min window) happen in the
%%        BFF or in the write queue?
%% =============================================================================

sequenceDiagram
    participant Member as Member (Mobile App)
    participant RN as React Native App
    participant BFF as BFF API (Node.js)
    participant WQ as Write Queue (2 req/sec)
    participant NAPI as Notion API (3 req/sec limit)
    participant NDB as Notion DBs (Trips, Components, Comments)

    rect rgb(20, 60, 80)
    Note over Member, NDB: Flow 1 - Trip Page Load
    Member->>RN: Opens trip page
    RN->>BFF: GET /trips/:id (Bearer JWT)
    BFF->>NAPI: Query Trips DB (page by ID)
    NAPI->>NDB: Read trip page
    NDB-->>NAPI: Trip data + component relations
    NAPI-->>BFF: Trip JSON
    BFF->>NAPI: Query Components DB (filter by trip)
    NAPI->>NDB: Read components
    NDB-->>NAPI: Components array
    NAPI-->>BFF: Components JSON
    BFF-->>RN: Combined response (trip + components + comments)
    RN-->>Member: Render phase-dependent view
    Note over RN: Start 60s polling cycle
    alt Error - Trip not found
        BFF-->>RN: 404 Not Found
        RN-->>Member: "Trip not available" screen
    end
    alt Error - Auth failure
        BFF-->>RN: 401 Unauthorized
        RN-->>Member: Redirect to login
    end
    end

    rect rgb(20, 70, 40)
    Note over Member, NDB: Flow 2 - Approve Component
    Member->>RN: Taps thumbs-up on component card
    RN->>RN: Optimistic UI update (green checkmark overlay)
    RN->>BFF: PATCH /trips/:id/components/:componentId/decision {decision: approved, decided_by: member_name}
    BFF->>WQ: Enqueue write (rate-limited 2 req/sec)
    WQ->>NAPI: Update Components page (Client Decision = Approved, Decision Date = now)
    NAPI->>NDB: Write Client Decision = Approved
    NDB-->>NAPI: 200 OK
    WQ->>NAPI: Create Task page (Component - Approved by Member, Priority: Normal)
    NAPI->>NDB: Write new task to Task Dashboard
    NDB-->>NAPI: 200 OK
    BFF-->>RN: 200 OK
    Note over RN: Next 60s poll confirms server state
    alt Error - Notion write fails
        NAPI-->>WQ: 500 / 429 Rate Limited
        WQ->>WQ: Retry 3x with exponential backoff
        WQ-->>BFF: Failure after retries
        BFF-->>RN: 500 Internal Server Error
        RN->>RN: Revert optimistic UI
        RN-->>Member: Toast - Could not save. Please try again.
    end
    end

    rect rgb(50, 40, 80)
    Note over Member, NDB: Flow 3 - Post Comment
    Member->>RN: Types and sends comment on component
    RN->>BFF: POST /trips/:id/components/:componentId/comments {comment: text, comment_type: client}
    BFF->>WQ: Enqueue write (rate-limited 2 req/sec)
    WQ->>NAPI: Create Comment page (Type=Client, Status=New, Component=relation)
    NAPI->>NDB: Write new comment to Component Comments DB
    NDB-->>NAPI: 201 Created
    WQ->>NAPI: Create Task page (Component - New comment from Member, Priority: Normal)
    NAPI->>NDB: Write new task to Task Dashboard
    NDB-->>NAPI: 201 Created
    BFF-->>RN: 201 Created
    RN-->>Member: Toast - Sent! Your advisor will be notified.
    alt Error - Comment write fails
        NAPI-->>WQ: 500 / 429 Rate Limited
        WQ->>WQ: Retry 3x with exponential backoff
        WQ-->>BFF: Failure after retries
        BFF-->>RN: 500 Internal Server Error
        RN-->>Member: Toast - Message not sent. Tap to retry.
    end
    end
